#-Function--ask.yn
  Function: ask.yn
      Desc: Ask y/n question,d return 0/1
          : NOTE: if verbose() is disabled, or there is no tty, ask.yn will
          : *always* return 0, without printing the string or waiting for a
          : response.
  Synopsis: ask.yn string
   Example: ask.yn "Continue?" || msg.die 'Not Continuing.'
#-Function--ask.yn------------------------------------------------------------
